=== ELEMENTAL_GATES ===
# id: 60
# title: The Elemental Gates
# chinese_title: 元素之门
# category: Puzzle
# mode: dungeon

Five doors stand before you, each marked with an elemental radical: fire, water, wood, metal, earth. The correct door changes based on a rotating cycle displayed on an overhead screen. Choose wrong, and a defense mechanism activates.

* [Analyze the cycle and choose the fire door]
  ~ gain_radical("火")
  "火" (huǒ) — fire, flame
* [Choose the water door — it counters fire]
  ~ gain_radical("水")
  "水" (shuǐ) — water
* [Choose the metal door for its defensive strength]
  ~ gain_radical("金")
  "金" (jīn) — metal, gold
* [Study the cycle longer to be certain]
  ~ gain_xp(15)
  "思" (sī) — to think, to consider
